    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add 60g <span class=\"text-purple\">[90g]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[120g]</span> <strong>flour</strong> to a bowl along with your<strong> cayenne pepper </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!), <strong>white wine vinegar</strong> and a very generous pinch of<strong> salt</strong></p><p>Add 80ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[120ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[160ml] </span><strong>very cold water</strong> and mix thoroughly – this is your <strong>spicy batter</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>panko breadcrumbs</strong> to a plate</p>",
