      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Dip the <strong>drained</strong> <strong>jumbo prawns</strong> in the spicy batter, tap off any excess, then add them to the panko breadcrumbs (turn several times to coat completely) – these are your <strong>breaded jumbo prawns</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1583249592662-x200.jpg",
