    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>shredded lettuce</strong> with the <strong>bang bang jumbo prawns</strong> on top</p><p>Drizzle over the <strong>zingy mayo</strong> and garnish with the <strong>chilli rounds</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and a <strong>lime wedge</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>chips</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
